palmetto south carolina’s highest civilian award in  was inducted into the south carolina business hall of fame in  and was named humanitarian of the year by the united way of the midlands in  mr smith holds a political science degree from the university of the south and graduated from the national commercial lending school at the university of oklahoma and the school of banking of the south at louisiana state university he served as member of the united states navy and naval reserves retiring in 8 with the rank of commander prior to joining the institute’s board mr smith served as chair of the longterm care taskforce which was convened by the institute during  and released  recommendations to improve the longterm care system and prepare it for the rapid growth in the aging population connect with imph join our mailing list sign up social media   south carolina institute of medicine and public health smith joel a iii top holdings whalewisdom search all search f filers only search sec filer search stocks only search mgmt inv cos only etfs only search active smith joel a iii • fremont ca how do i update this listing smith joel a iii is based out of fremont whalewisdom has at least  insider transactions form  in our database for smith joel a iii summary dg insider form  create email alert × email notification log in or signup to see more advanced email alert options such as selecting any type of sec form multiple filers or classes of filers and much more or to simply have an email sent to you whenever we receive a new f filing from smith joel a iii enter your email address below and choose submit your email cancel contact info smith joel a iii  encyclopedia circle fremont ca     business phone 8 8 sec sic codesemiconductors  related devices recent sec filings  filed on   filed on   filed on   filed on 8  filed on   filed on  schedule d and g events since  subscription required form   nonderivative insider transactions since  loading elevate your investments try it for 